                <p>Built on the Omega-Arc platform, the Harrier EV is expected to inherit Tata’s high safety standards. It’s likely to come with:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">6 airbags (standard on top trims) </span> </li>
                    <li><span class="font-weight-700">Electronic Stability Program (ESP) </span></li>
